title: A home with a personal touch - Res Lease in Round Rock. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Check out this lovely 3-bedroom single-story home located on the northeast side of Round Rock!', "You will really appreciate the home's open floorplan, the floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace, plush carpeted flooring, and designated breakfast area.", 'The well-designed kitchen features laminate countertops, a dishwasher, gas stove, and ample cabinetry.', 'The home also features a 2-car attached garage and a big fenced patio with lots of space!', 'See this wonderful home for yourself!', '**', 'In person tours required (no exceptions)', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 1367256)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
